'''Google, Inc''' {{nasdaq|GOOG}}, is a [[United States|U.S.]] public corporation, initially established as a privately-held corporation in [[1998]], that designed and manages the Internet [[Google search]] engine. Google's corporate headquarters is at the "[[Googleplex]]" in [[Mountain View, Santa Clara County, California|Mountain View]], [[California]] and employs over 4,000 workers. [[Eric Schmidt|Dr. Eric Schmidt]], former [[CEO]] of [[Novell]], was named the Chief Executive Officer when co-founder [[Lawrence E. Page|Larry Page]] stepped down. Google is widely known as the best and most effective serch engine on the World Wide Web. Many people use it, including myself. Google has several other programs like gmail and google earth which are especially usefull!
